
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Adishow";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_PageLayout.cshtml";
}
<section id="services" class="section-bg" style="margin-top:50px">
    <div class="container">

        <header class="section-header">
            <h3>Media Presentation</h3>
            <h2>AdiShow</h2>
            <p>To explore your entire capabilities, services and products in detail for your visitors and express your identity more and more, Adishow is the most perfect solution. This application presents all the available content to engage the audience and attract their attention!</p>
            <h3>Adishow Features</h3>
        </header>

        <div class="row justify-content-center align-items-center">

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 wow bounceInUp" data-wow-duration="1.4s">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="icon" style="background: #fceef3;"><i class="fa fa-users" style="color: #ff689b;"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="title"><a href="">Multi-user</a></h4>
                    <p class="description">It is easily possible to have a multi-user collaborative experience for up to 4 users at the same time who all can interact with different content.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 wow bounceInUp" data-wow-duration="1.4s">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="icon" style="background: #fff0da;"><i class="fa fa-star-half" style="color: #e98e06;"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="title"><a href="">engaging metrics</a></h4>
                    <p class="description">based on our machine-learning model, we have point values for different actions,  and customer interaction is measurable with what we’ve learned from the data across  customers’ events.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 wow bounceInUp" data-wow-delay="0.1s" data-wow-duration="1.4s">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="icon" style="background: #e6fdfc;"><i class="fa fa-telegram" style="color: #3fcdc7;"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="title"><a href="">Sharing Options</a></h4>
                    <p class="description">Users can share any media files such as image or video via Email which is a great tool for capturing data.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 wow bounceInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s" data-wow-duration="1.4s">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="icon" style="background: #e1eeff;"><i class="fa fa-info" style="color: #2282ff;"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="title"><a href="">Info Box</a></h4>
                    <p class="description">Your important information about any of your media can be attached using pop up text box. This feature  engage more efficiently your visitors to your products and services.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 wow bounceInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s" data-wow-duration="1.4s">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="icon" style="background: #ecebff;"><i class="fa fa-bar-chart" style="color: #8660fe;"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="title"><a href="">Audience Analytics</a></h4>
                    <p class="description">The behavior of your visitors are analyzed through their interactions with the application.A statistics dashboard is available to monitor all audience interactions to make useful reports for future decision. Information like number of visitors, most favorites media, most shared files.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 wow bounceInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s" data-wow-duration="1.4s">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="icon" style="background: #ecebff;"><i class="fa fa-edit" style="color: #8660fe;"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="title"><a href="">On-Screen Whiteboard</a></h4>
                    <p class="description">it is used to put notes everywhere in a presentation to draw around important area and subject.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4 wow bounceInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s" data-wow-duration="1.4s">
                <div class="box">
                    <div class="icon" style="background: #ecebff;"><i class="fa fa-qrcode" style="color: #8660fe;"></i></div>
                    <h4 class="title"><a href="">Quick QR Code Sharing</a></h4>
                    <p class="description">any files can be shared by scanning the QR Code of them using smart phones to access to any media which permitted by company. This is very cost-effective to replace for conventional printed catalogs and brochures.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <h2>Are You Ready for excitement?</h2>
            <p>A common problem in every booth would be that they do not have enough space to present all products. Therefore, Adishow is the best solution for the audience to have a digital interactive experience. It supports all types of images and videos, and you can describe your products with on-screen whiteboard tools. Adishow can throw content around the screen, enlarge images, and flick through PDFs.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/img/Adinux/all-devices.png" alt="First slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/img/Adinux/PicMagic1.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/img/Adinux/ShowTime.jpg" alt="Second slide">
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</section><!-- #services -->
